  "screens": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "交易做出去以后，",
        "接下来最扎心的问题只剩一个。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "你到底赚了，还是亏了？",
        "这就是 **<term id=\"pnl\">盈亏</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "pnl"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "pnl"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "如果你是多头，",
        "价格往上通常更有利。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "pnl"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "type": "formula",
      "lines": [
        "多头未实现盈亏可以先这样看。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "pnl"
      ],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "\\text{PnL}_{\\text{long}}=\\text{Quantity}\\times(P_{\\text{bid}}-P_{\\text{entry}})",
        "spoken": "数量乘以当前买价减去入场价。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "如果你是空头，",
        "方向就反过来了。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "pnl"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "type": "formula",
      "lines": [
        "空头未实现盈亏常写成这样。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "pnl"
      ],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "\\text{PnL}_{\\text{short}}=-\\text{Quantity}\\times(P_{\\text{ask}}-P_{\\text{entry}})",
        "spoken": "先算当前卖空回补成本和入场价的差，再乘数量并带上反号。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "先别怕公式。",
        "只看方向就行。"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "如果你做多之后价格上涨，多头未实现盈亏通常怎样变化？",
        "options": [
          "更可能增加",
          "更可能减少",
          "一定不变"
        ],
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "多头的核心是低买高卖，价格上涨通常会抬高未实现盈亏。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "但仓位没平掉之前，",
        "很多盈亏都还只是账面上的。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "这就引出 **<term id=\"mark_to_market\">盯市计价</term>**。",
        "也就是按当前市场价格重新估值。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "mark_to_market"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "mark_to_market"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "它不是看你最初花了多少钱。",
        "而是看你现在如果立刻平仓，大概值多少。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "mark_to_market"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "接着还要看系统怎么记账。",
        "有的系统按订单记，有的按净持仓记。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "**<term id=\"order_based_system\">订单制系统</term>** 把每笔单子分开看。",
        "它们不急着彼此抵消。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "order_based_system"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "order_based_system"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "**<term id=\"position_based_system\">持仓制系统</term>** 更关心净头寸。",
        "订单之间可以互相对冲。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "position_based_system"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "position_based_system"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "很多持仓制系统还会按 **<term id=\"fifo\">先进先出</term>** 处理。",
        "先开的仓位先配对平掉。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "fifo"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "fifo"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "这里先抓住一个区别。",
        "哪一种更关心“净持仓”而不是“每张单” ？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "选一个。",
        "options": [
          "订单制系统",
          "持仓制系统",
          "两者完全一样"
        ],
        "answer": 1,
        "explanation": "持仓制系统更关心对冲后的净结果。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "最后是最容易让收益和风险一起放大的东西。",
        "**<term id=\"leverage\">杠杆</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "leverage"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "leverage"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "杠杆不是凭空送钱。",
        "它是用更少自有资金，撬动更大头寸。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "leverage"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "支撑它的缓冲垫，",
        "就是 **<term id=\"margin\">保证金</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "margin"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "margin"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "当市场规定你至少要押多少，",
        "那就是 **<term id=\"margin_requirement\">保证金要求</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "margin_requirement"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "margin_requirement"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "type": "formula",
      "lines": [
        "杠杆和保证金的关系，可以先记住这一条。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "leverage",
        "margin_requirement"
      ],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "\\text{Leverage Ratio}=\\frac{1}{\\text{Margin Requirement}}",
        "spoken": "保证金要求越低，能开的杠杆通常越高。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "进一步，账户还能买多少，",
        "就是 **<term id=\"buying_power\">购买力</term>**。"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "buying_power"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "buying_power"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "type": "formula",
      "lines": [
        "它常写成下面这样。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "buying_power",
        "leverage"
      ],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "\\text{Buying Power}=\\text{Leverage Ratio}\\times \\text{Investor Equity}",
        "spoken": "购买力等于杠杆倍数乘上账户权益。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "所以这一段真正想让你记住的是：",
        "杠杆会放大机会，也会放大错误。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "leverage"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "最后做个判断。",
        "保证金要求越低，通常意味着什么？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "选一个最贴近公式含义的答案。",
        "options": [
          "杠杆通常更高",
          "杠杆通常更低",
          "购买力一定变成零"
        ],
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "在其他条件不变时，保证金要求越低，可使用的杠杆通常越高。"
      }
    }
  ],
